features: Fine Motor Skills Toys:Dinosaur number matching set is designed for toddlers,the kid-friendly size and smooth center connection make it easy for toddlers to hold and put together the little dino, designed to promote fine motor skill development. By picking up the corresponding numbers and snapping them together, their hand-eye coordination and finger dexterity are improved, and the tactile nature of the game also engages toddler sense of touch, further enhancing their sensory development.

Number Matching Dinosaur Game:Montessori dinosaur number matching fine motor toy for Toddlers - a fun and educational toys designed to help toddlers learn numbers while developing their sensory and fine motor skills, double-sided design for easy matching and Disassembles to provide a hands-on learning experience for kids.

Number Matching Set: Designed for toddlers aged 18 months and older.Each dinosaur is labeled with a number and accompanied by a corresponding number of shapes, promoting early learning of numbers and quantities. With 10 dinosaurs available in 9 vibrant colors and 3 different dinosaur types, children can engage in fun activities such as observing, classifying, and matching based on colors, shapes, or numbers. Additionally, the set comes with a convenient drawstring bag for easy storage.

Quantity and Numerals: Help your child grasp the concept of numbers effortlessly. One side showcases cute dinosaurs with corresponding quantities of spots, making number recognition tangible. Flip them over to find clear English numerals, assisting in numerical association and reinforcement.

Versatile Learning Tool: Suitable for both home and school environments, this toy is perfect for toddlers, preschoolers, and kindergarteners. It offers a versatile learning experience that introduces quantity, numerals, colors, and basic math concepts in a captivating and memorable way.

reviews.reviewTitle: 3.0 out of 5 stars It's okay, However....
reviews.reviewText: Either the title deceived me or I received the wrong item. When I placed my order I order the 26pcs letter with numbers dinosaurs. However, the item that I received was only dinosaurs numbers.My kids love dinosaurs and loved these dino numbers but they really also wanted the dino letters.They are great; my kids like to mix and match them and counting along the way. Colors are nice and bright! It could have more of a variety of dinosaurs though, in my opinion! It's a good toy and the kids like the dinosaurs.The only con is that I did not receive the alphabet dinosaurs; which was a little disappointing!
